%A0%20Corp.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMurdoch%20will%20exit%20his%20role%20in%20November.%20His%20eldest%20son%2C%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%2C%20will%20be%20his%20successor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20memo%20to%20staff%2C%20Murdoch%20wrote%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BOur%20companies%20are%20in%20robust%20health%2C%20as%20am%20I.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMedia%20mogul%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frupert-murdoch-stepping-down-fox-news-son-lachlan-taking-over-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20he%20is%20stepping%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20his%20role%20as%20chairman%20at%20News%20Corp.%20and%20Fox%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2092-year-old%20billionaire's%20departure%20will%20leave%20Lachlan%20Murdoch%2C%20his%20eldest%20son%2C%20as%20the%20sole%20chair%20of%20News%20Corp.%20Lachlan%20is%20also%20the%20executive%20chair%20and%20CEO%20of%20Fox%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20News%20Corp%20until%20it%20was%20split%20from%20the%20company%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20my%20entire%20professional%20life%2C%20I%20have%20been%20engaged%20daily%20with%20news%20and%20ideas%2C%20and%20that%20will%20not%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Murdoch%20wrote%20in%20the%20memo%20that%20was%20sent%20to%20his%20employees.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20time%20is%20right%20for%20me%20to%20take%20on%20different%20roles%2C%20knowing%20that%20we%20have%20truly%20talented%20teams%20and%20a%20passionate%2C%20principled%20leader%20in%20Lachlan%20who%20will%20become%20sole%20Chairman%20of%20both%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurdoch%20started%20out%20in%20the%20newspaper%20business%20in%20the%201950s%20and%20later%20purchased%20Twentieth%20Century%20Fox%20in%201985%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20US%20television%20stations%20in%201986%2C%20creating%20Fox%20Broadcasting.%20The%20billionaire's%20media%20empire%20includes%20most%20notably%20Fox%20News%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20below.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Colleagues%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20writing%20to%20let%20you%20all%20know%20that%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20transition%20to%20the%20role%20of%20Chairman%20Emeritus%20at%20Fox%20and%20News.%20For%20my%20entire%20professional%20life%2C%20I%20have%20been%20engaged%20daily%20with%20news%20and%20ideas%2C%20and%20that%20will%20not%20change.%20But%20the%20time%20is%20right%20for%20me%20to%20take%20on%20different%20roles%2C%20knowing%20that%20we%20have%20truly%20talented%20teams%20and%20a%20passionate%2C%20principled%20leader%20in%20Lachlan%20who%20will%20become%20sole%20Chairman%20of%20both%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20excessive%20pride%20nor%20false%20humility%20are%20admirable%20qualities.%20But%20I%20am%20truly%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20have%20achieved%20collectively%20through%20the%20decades%2C%20and%20I%20owe%20much%20to%20my%20colleagues%2C%20whose%20contributions%20to%20our%20success%20have%20sometimes%20been%20unseen%20outside%20the%20company%20but%20are%20deeply%20appreciated%20by%20me.%20Whether%20the%20truck%20drivers%20distributing%20our%20papers%2C%20the%20cleaners%20who%20toil%20when%20we%20have%20left%20the%20office%2C%20the%20assistants%20who%20support%20us%20or%20the%20skilled%20operators%20behind%20the%20cameras%20or%20the%20computer%20code%2C%20we%20would%20be%20less%20successful%20and%20have%20less%20positive%20impact%20on%20society%20without%20your%20day-after-day%20dedication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20companies%20are%20in%20robust%20health%2C%20as%20am%20I.%20Our%20opportunities%20far%20exceed%20our%20commercial%20challenges.%20We%20have%20every%20reason%20to%20be%20optimistic%20about%20the%20coming%20years%20%E2%80%94%20I%20certainly%20am%2C%20and%20plan%20to%20be%20here%20to%20participate%20in%20them.%20But%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20the%20freedom%20of%20thought%2C%20has%20never%20been%20more%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20f