20government%20or%20the%20BJP%20before%202014%20knows%20that%20other%20parties%20are%20several%20light%20years%20behind%20the%20current%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%20in%20several%20states%20for%20decades%20now%2C%20but%20its%20approach%20towards%20the%20media%20has%20drastically%20changed%20since%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202012%2C%20immediately%20after%20the%20killings%20of%2017%20Adivasis%20in%20CRPF%20firing%20in%20Bastar%2C%20a%20weekly%20placed%20a%20photograph%20of%20the%20then-home%20minister%20with%20the%20corpses%20and%20asked%20on%20its%20cover%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20Chidambaram%20sleep%20well%20at%20night%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20has%20been%20burning%20for%20several%20months%2C%20with%20the%20death%20toll%20many%20times%20more%20than%20the%20Bastar%20incident.%20How%20many%20media%20houses%20can%20now%20give%20a%20similar%20headline%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20enabled%20the%20media%20to%20directly%20name%20the%20senior-most%20UPA%20leaders%3F%20With%20all%20their%20flaws%2C%20they%20at%20least%20had%20the%20humility%20to%20accept%20their%20failures.%20Following%20a%20deadly%20Naxal%20attack%20in%202010%2C%20P.%20Chidambaram%20repeatedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchidambaram-buck-stops-with-me-take-full-responsibility-414884%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20buck%20stops%20at%20my%20desk%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20the%20incumbent%20home%20minister%20ever%20say%20so%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Manipur%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFreelancers%20versus%20established%20houses%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20of%20those%20opposing%20the%20list%20have%20asked%20for%20calling%20out%20the%20bad%20names.%20They%20can%20look%20within.%20How%20many%20stories%20have%20they%20done%20to%20call%20out%20the%20%E2%80%98journalism%E2%80%99%20of%20these%2014%20or%20countless%20similar%20names%20or%20their%20media%20houses%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20duty%20to%20expose%20the%20hateful%20agenda%20of%20these%20media%20houses%20is%20largely%20fulfilled%20by%20new%20fact-checkers%2C%20whom%20the%20established%20names%20are%20not%20even%20comfortable%20admitting%20into%20their%20pantheon%20of%20journalists.%20There%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20fact-checking%20organisations%20comprising%20a%20handful%20of%20young%20people%2C%20had%20the%20bigger%20institutions%20taken%20it%20upon%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVeterans%20often%20express%20the%20need%20to%20cleanse%20the%20media.%20But%20who%20will%20do%20it%2C%20if%20not%20they%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20column%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20at%20all%20argue%20that%20all%20those%20who%20oppose%20the%20list%20are%20either%20complicit%20with%20the%20government%20or%20have%20been%20cowed%20down.%20But%20a%20division%20between%20two%20broad%20sections%20in%20Indian%20media%20is%20discernible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20Call%20for%20Boycott%20of%20Newspapers%20Spreading%20Hatred%20Resonates%20With%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Decision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20has%20accepted%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20believe%20grudgingly%2C%20restrictions%20on%20their%20pen%20in%20order%20to%20adjust%20themselves%20to%20the%20present%20political%20climate%2C%20and%20hence%20will%20ask%20fewer%20questions%20and%20avoid%20naming%20or%20targeting%20certain%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20others%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20accept%20any%20such%20restrictions%20that%20dilute%20their%20press%20freedom%20under%20Article%2019%20of%20the%20constitution.%20To%20know%20more%20about%20the%20adjustments%2C%20just%20check%20their%20journalism%20record%20before%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20comprises%20mostly%20established%20institutions%20with%20honourable%20bylines%20and%20impeccable%20editorial%20expertise%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20are%20mostly%20those%20with%20limited%20resources%20but%20who%20have%20done%20exemplary%20work%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%2C%20therefore%2C%20raise%20a%20question%20for%20the%20former%3A%20why%20is%20it%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20investigations%20concerning%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20spanning%20from%20coal%20deals%20and%20Adani%20to%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20hate%20speech%2C%20have%20originated%20from%20freelancers%20or%20organizations%20with%20limited%20budgets%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20tragedy%20of%20Indian%20journalism%20that%20most%20of%20these%20freelancers%20have%20a%20body%20of%20work%20behind%20them%2C%20but%20they%20find%20themselves%20not%20merely%20unemployed%2C%20but%20unemployable%20under%20the%20present%20political%20climate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%2080%25%20of%20those%20working%20in%20the%20media%20and%20publishing%20industry%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs%20in%20a%20span%20of%20five%20years%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Findia%2Falmost-78-per-cent-jobs-lost-in-media-and-publishing-industry-in-5-years-cmie-survey%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy.%C2%A0The%20industry%20employed%20over%2010.3%20lakh%20people%20in%20September%202016%2C%20which%20came%20down%20to%20a%20mere%202.3%20lakh%20in%20August%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20now%20has%20fewer%20journalists%20to%20hold%20the%20government%20accountable.%20Unemployment%20in%20the%20media%20sector%20dilutes%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20k