FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20higher%20share%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20are%20stressed%20or%20burned%20out%20%3Cstrong%3Ein%20the%20past%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20than%20fully%20remote%20workers%2C%20Deloitte%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EDeloitte's%20Jana%20Arbanas%20said%20some%20of%20this%20may%20be%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20structure%20as%20a%20hybrid%20worker.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EYet%2C%20many%20hybrid%20workers%20are%20content%20with%20their%20jobs%2C%20Deloitte%20survey%20results%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20hybrid%20work%20model%20may%20be%20the%20dream%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-making-workers-employees-return-to-office-rto-wfh-hybrid-2023-1%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%3C%2Fa%3E%20scenario%20for%20many%20companies%20right%20now%2C%20it%20may%20be%20stressing%20out%20some%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHybrid%20workers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20feel%20disconnected%20from%20on-site%20colleagues%20and%20say%20that%20their%20collaboration%20efforts%20are%20ineffective%2C%20and%20they're%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20distracted%20by%20nonwork%20activities%2C%20to%20have%20difficulty%20accessing%20work%20files%2C%20to%20feel%20stress%20and%20burnout%2C%20and%20to%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20prioritizing%20their%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20recent%20Deloitte%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJana%20Arbanas%2C%20vice%20chair%20and%20Deloitte's%20US%20Telecom%2C%20Media%2C%20and%20Entertainment%20sector%20leader%2C%20told%20Insider%C2%A0that%20the%20hybrid%20model%2C%20which%20can%20mean%20working%20a%20few%20days%20in%20an%20office%20and%20the%20other%20days%20remotely%2C%20is%20still%20pretty%20new.%20People%20may%20still%20be%20adjusting%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20basically%20creating%20a%20unique%20schedule%20each%20and%20every%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Arbanas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20schedule%20then%20has%20diversity%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20a%20given%20day%20looks%20like.%20I%20do%20think%20that%20that%20lack%20of%20structure%20that%20many%20people%20who%20are%20navigating%20this%20hybrid%20return%20to%20work%20is%20causing%20some%20of%20that%20additional%20stress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Finsights%2Findustry%2Ftelecommunications%2Fconnectivity-mobile-trends-survey.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeloitte%202023%20Connected%20Consumer%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20asked%20about%20problems%20and%20feelings%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months%20while%20working%20from%20home.%20Deloitte%20clarified%20to%20Insider%20that%20a%20hybrid%20respondent%20was%20likely%20basing%20their%20answers%20on%20how%20they%20are%20feeling%20overall%2C%20not%20just%20problems%20when%20they%20are%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20shared%20results%20from%20the%20Deloitte%20survey%20to%20Insider%20were%20based%20on%20nearly%20240%20fully%20remote%20workers%2C%20around%20350%20hybrid%20workers%2C%20and%20about%20460%20fully%20in-person%20workers%20and%20was%20conducted%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20higher%20share%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20said%20that%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months%20they%20were%20feeling%20stressed%20or%20burned%20out%20than%20those%20who%20were%20fully%20remote%2C%2040%25%20vs%2030%25%20respectively.%20Just%20over%20a%20third%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20also%20felt%20they%20didn't%20really%20have%20enough%20time%20for%20wellness%2C%20while%20almost%20a%20quarter%20of%20fully%20remote%20workers%20felt%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20quarter%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20said%20they%20felt%20disconnected%20from%20their%20on-site%20colleagues%20compared%20to%2013%25%20of%20fully%20remote%20workers.%20Similarly%2C%20almost%20a%20quarter%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20felt%20there%20was%20ineffective%20collaboration%20happening%20compared%20to%209%25%20of%20fully%20remote%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20possible%20that%20without%20structure%2C%20a%20hybrid%20worker%20shows%20up%20to%20work%20and%20none%20of%20their%20colleagues%20are%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Arbanas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20chosen%20the%20day%20that%20everyone%20else%20has%20chosen%20to%20be%20at%20home.%20And%20so%20they're%20not%20actually%20even%20getting%20the%20benefit%20of%20being%20on%20site%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20perhaps%20of%20structure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20those%20working%20at%20a%20workplace%20all%20the%20time%20or%20people%20working%20remotely%20each%20workday%20might%20not%20feel%20this%20lack%20of%20a%20work%20structure.%20Arbanas%20said%20for%20fully%20remote%20workers%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Binherently%20have%20probably%20built%20a%20structure%20that%20works%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20when%20they%20can%20be%20distracted%20by%20or%20doing%20activities%20not%20related%20to%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20those%20stresses%2C%20a%20high%20share%20of%20hybrid%20workers%20were%20satisfied%20in%20their%20jobs.%20The%20Deloitte%20survey%20found%2072%25%20of%20hybrid%20workers%2C%2070%25%20of%20fully%20remote%20workers%2C%20and%2063%25%20of%20those%20who%20work%20in%20person%20full%20time%20felt%20either%20good%20or%20extremely%20good%20about%20their%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20hybrid%20structure%20does%20create%20the%20most%20satisfaction%20because%20you're%20getting%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%2C%26quot%3B%20Arbanas%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20enabling%20employees%20to%20get%20greater%20flexibility%2C%20and%20whether%20that%20takes%20the%20shape%20of%20getting%20to%20focus%20on%20your%20wellbeing%2C%20spend%20a%20bit%20more%20time%20with%20family%20because%20you're%20not%20commuting%2C%20those%20are%20real%2C%20meaningful%20impacts%20to%20an%20individual's%20work%20life.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20also%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%2C%20do%20some%20of%20that%20innovation%2C%20do%20some%20of%20that%20connectedness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeloitte%20found%20almost%20half%20of%20hybrid%20workers%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20felt%20their%20relationships%20with%20family%20either%20somewhat%20or%20significantly%20was%20better%20than%20when%20they%20used%20to%20be%20working%20in%20person%20all%20the%20time.%20The%20share%20of%20fully%20remote%20workers%20who%20said%20this%20was%2038%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20told%20Insider%20that%20remote%20work%20in%20general%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20continue%2C%20and%20companies%20have%20shared%20with%20Insider%20why%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-microsoft-ibm-companies-hybrid-work-office-collaboration-flexibility-happiness-2023-8%5C%22%3Echosen%20to%20have%20workers%20be%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20with%20clients%20part%20of%20the%20time.%20Arbanas%20also%20thinks%20the%20hybrid%20model%20is%20staying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20can%20be%20this%20sweet%20spot%20of%20achieving%20what%20an%20organization%20is%20looking%20for%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20they%20need%20from%20their%20employees%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20providing%20flexibility%20for%20employees%20that%20didn't%20exist%20previously%2C%26quot%3B%20Arbanas%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20like%20working%20in%20the%20office%2C%20remotely%2C%20or%20a%20hybrid%20schedule%3F%20Have%20you%20made%20a%20career%20move%20to%20achieve%20this%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-hybrid-workers-remote-employees-are-feeling-deloitte-