20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20our%20side%2C%20specific%20evidence%20about%20criminal%20activities%20by%20individuals%20based%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20has%20been%20shared%20with%20Canada%20but%20not%20acted%20upon...Yes%2C%20I%20do%20think%20there%20is%20a%20degree%20of%20prejudice%20here.%20They%20have%20made%20allegations%20and%20taken%20action%20on%20them.%20To%20us%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20these%20allegations%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Canada%20are%20primarily%20politically%20driven%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695296280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-01%2Fmodi-trudeau_650x400_71516730530.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-parity-india-seeks-reduction-of-canadian-diplomats-amid-huge-row-4410715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20asked%20Canada%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20India%20citing%20%26quot%3Binterference%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20Indian%20affairs%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-parity-india-seeks-reduction-of-canadian-diplomats-amid-huge-row-4410715%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-parity-india-seeks-reduction-of-canadian-diplomats-amid-huge-row-4410715%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-parity-india-seeks-reduction-of-canadian-diplomats-amid-huge-row-4410715%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indigo%20passenger%20tries%20to%20open%20flight%20door%20mid-air%3B%20arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695295909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103841071%2Cimgsize-19426.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagartala%2Ftripura-man-arrested-for-attempt-to-open-flight-door-