0and%20Canada%20announcing%20it%20would%20reduce%20its%20diplomatic%20staff%20presence%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20wants%20Canada%20to%20reduce%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20as%20they%20have%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20staff%20in%20India%20than%20India%20has%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20asking%20Canada%20to%20take%20action%20against%20over%2020%20individuals%20linked%20to%20Khalistani%20terrorism%2C%20Mr%20Bagchi%20said.%20He%20said%20Canada%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20safe%20havens%20for%20terrorists%2C%20adding%20the%20hold%20on%20Canadian%20visa%20processing%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20larger%20issue%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20should%20worry%20about%20its%20growing%20reputation%20of%20being%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20extremists%20and%20terrorists%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20by%20Canada%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B%20and%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20move%20to%20Ottawa's%20expulsion%20of%20an%20Indian%20official%20over%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20two%20masked%20assailants%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20he%20presided%20over%20in%20Surrey%2C%20an%20outer%20suburb%20of%20Vancouver.%20He%20was%20wanted%20by%20India%20over%20terrorism%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20accuses%20Ottawa%20of%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20activities%20of%20radical%20Sikh%20nationalists%20who%20advocate%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20independent%20state%20to%20be%20carved%20out%20of%20northern%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695295800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2F477nnk8_moditrudeau650_625x300_22_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallegations-by-canada-pol