2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress's%20Derek%20O%20Brien%20today%20gave%20two%20options%20to%20the%20Centre%20on%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20assemblies.%20Speaking%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20women's%20quota%20bill%2C%20he%20said%20the%20government%20should%20bring%20the%20bill%20in%202024%2C%20or%20give%20women%20quota%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Tucked%20in%20it%20was%20a%20third%20option%20--%20let%20the%20BJP%20get%20one-third%20women%20elected%20from%20their%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20point%3A%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20serious%20about%20empowering%20women%20--%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20one%20thing%20to%20give%20tickets.%20Another%20to%20give%20tickets%20that%20are%20winnable%26quot%3B.%20This%20he%20elucidated%20through%20two%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202021%2C%20before%20Bengal%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20men%20came%20money%2C%20media%2C%20muscle%20power%2C%20misogyny%20and%20mocked%20her.%20Didi%20O%20Didi.%C2%A0%20You%20broke%20her%20foot.%20Smashed%20it.%20she%20gave%20you%20an%20answer%20truely%20like%20a%20woman.%20softly.%20The%20people%20of%20Bengal%20answered%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20O'Brien%20said%20in%20a%20job%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20election%20what%20happened%3F%20Bengal's%20health%20ministry%2C%20finance%20ministry%2C%20land%2C%20industry%2C%20commerce%20ministries%20are%20all%20headed%20by%20women.%20You%20could%20not%20find%20one%20woman%20in%2016%20NDA%20states%20for%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20other%20example%20was%20from%20a%20news%20report%20that%20quoted%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20as%20saying%20that%20men%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20gods%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20achieve%20womanly%20qualities%2C%20and%20women%2C%20when%20they%20develop%20masculine%20qualities%2C%20become%20%26quot%3Brakshas%20(demons)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20build%20a%20new%20building%2C%20but%20first%20you%20need%20to%20change%20your%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20historic%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%20which%20envisages%20giving%2033%20per%20cent%20seats%20to%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20which%20was%20in%20freeze%20for%20decades%2C%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday.%20It%20got%20support%20from%20across%20the%20board%2C%20with%20only%20two%20MPS%20voting%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20presented%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today.%20While%20the%20Opposition%20agrees%20in%20principle%20with%20the%20reservation%2C%20they%20refuse%20to%20accept%20the%20government's%20time%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reservation%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20after%20a%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20which%2C%20under%20Constitution's%20Article%2082%2C%20can%20be%20conducted%20after%202026%2C%20which%20pushes%20the%20implementation%20to%202029%20or%20beyond.%20While%20the%20government%20has%20said%20that%20the%20census%20and%20delimitation%20will%20begin%20after%20next%20year's%20general%20election%2C%20implementing%20quota%20sooner%20may%20call%20for%20fresh%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695295560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fkvd5or14_derek-obrien_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-1-woman-chief-minister-in-16-nda-states-derek-obrien-on-womens-quota-4410744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress's%20Derek%20O%20Brien%20today%20gave%20two%20options%20to%20the%20Centre%20on%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20assemblies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-1-woman-chief-minister-in-16-nda-states-derek-obrien-on-womens-quota-4410744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22h