%20spotted%20by%20a%20license%20plate%20reader%20in%20Catoosa%2C%20Oklahoma.%20When%20officers%20tried%20to%20stop%20the%20vehicle%2C%20it%20sped%20away%20and%20crashed.%C2%A0The%20vehicle%20ultimately%20caught%20fire%20and%20officers%20at%20the%20scene%20reported%20hearing%20noises%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20two%20gunshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Huey%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20critically%20wounded%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat%2C%20Mr%20Burne%20said.%20Both%20had%20gunshot%20wounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20Illinois%20woman%20whose%20mother%20dated%20Huey%20for%208%20years%2C%20called%20him%20a%20''very%20dangerous%20man%2C''%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fsuspect-chicago-area-familys-killing-was-dangerous-man-woman-lived-say-rcna108128%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20and%20their%20three%20pets%20were%20all%20shot%20to%20death%20in%20what%20police%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20random%20incident.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvidence%20has%20shown%20us%20a%20nexus%20between%20our%20suspects%20and%20the%20victims%20as%20well%20as%20possible%20motives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Burne%20said%20at%20the%20conference%2C%20without%20elaborating%20on%20that%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''This%20is%20still%20an%20active%20and%20evolving%20investigation%20and%20this%20portion%20of%20the%20incident%20is%20still%20unfolding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20Burne%20added.%20The%20police%20also%C2%A0said%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20there%20are%20other%20suspects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20family%20of%20Zoraida%20Bartolomei%2C%20one%20of%20the%20four%20victims%20in%20the%20killings%2C%20issued%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20express%20our%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20for%20the%20outpouring%20of%20solidarity%20and%20support%20following%20the%20tragic%20loss.%20At%20this%20moment%2C%20our%20primary%20focus%20is%20on%20channeling%20support%2C%20assistance%2C%20and%20love%20for%20our%20family%20and%20loved%20ones.%20We%20appreciate%20the%20understanding%20and%20we%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20once%20again%20express%20our%20profound%20gratitude%20for%20the%20solidarity%20and%20support%20extended%20by%20people%20during%20this%20period%2C%20''%20the%20family%20said%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcchicago.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Ffamily-of-victims-slain-in-romeoville-shooting-issues-statement%2F3232935%2F%5C%22%3ENBC%20Chicago%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695292980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F83cnauvg_us-couple-and-their-two-young-children_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suspected-of-killing-chicago-family-their-dogs-found-dead-after-car-crash-4410441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2231-year-old%20Nathaniel%20Huey%20Jr.%20and%20an%20unnamed%20woman%2C%20who%20were%20identified%20as%20persons%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20killings%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20car%20crash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suspected-of-killing-chicago-family-their-dogs-found-dead-after-car-crash-4410441%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suspected-of-killing-chicago-family-their-dogs-found-dead-after-car-crash-4410441%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suspected-of-killing-chicago-family-their-dogs-found-dead-after-car-crash-4410441%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Badal%20meets%20Shah%3B%20says%20Punjabis%20in%20panic%20over%20India-Canada%20ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695292704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fp