ecurity.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20justice%20in%20sight%20for%20those%20who%20walked%20kilometres%20barefoot%2C%20those%20who%20lost%20jobs%2C%20and%20those%20who%20had%20no%20food%20security%20in%20place.%20Trapped%20in%20a%20loop%20of%20suffering%20so%20severe%20it%20continues%20to%20this%20day%2C%20they%20struggle%20to%20find%20means%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20refuses%20to%20take%20accountability%20for%20its%20poor%20planning%20and%20its%20consequences%2C%20and%20encourages%20people%20to%20move%20past%20it.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet%20and%20steady%20their%20lives%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20were%20left%20homeless%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20as%20close%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcommissioned-citizens-report-g20-preparations-leave-thousands-homeless-in-india%2Farticle67131721.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520the%2520findings%252C%2520the%2C%252C%2520and%2520Ghiyaspur%252C%2520among%2520others.%5C%22%3E2.5-3%20lakh%20%3C%2Fa%3Epeople%20were%20evicted.%20This%20number%20is%20attributed%20to%20only%20a%20few%20states.%20One%20could%20only%20imagine%20the%20number%20if%20all%20the%20states%20were%20taken%20into%20account.%20The%20state%20is%20not%20ignorant%20of%20the%20pandemic-induced%20struggles.%20Even%20so%2C%20they%20are%20adding%20to%20the%20distress%20with%20these%20evictions%20in%20the%20name%20of%20beautification.%20The%20message%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%3A%20%E2%80%9CMove%20on%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20seek%20accountability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20struggles%20during%20the%20pandemic%20were%20primarily%20related%20to%20health%20and%20death%2C%20both%20still%20quantifiable%2C%20the%20distress%20it%20caused%2C%20especially%20in%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20is%20immense.%20In%20order%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20distress%20continuing%20to%20be%20faced%20by%20marginalised%20sections%20as%20the%20pandemic%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20their%20lives%2C%20between%202021%20and%202023%20the%20Public%20Inquiry%20Committee%2FPeople%E2%80%99s%20Commission%20conducted%2013%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcovidtruths.in%2F%5C%22%3Epublic%20hearings%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETales%20of%20many%20forms%20of%20distress%20faced%20by%20the%20street%20vending%20community%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fas-the-impact-of-lockdown-yet-to-wear-off-delhi-street-vendors-travails-persist%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20there%20are%20around%203%2C00%2C000%20street%20vendors%20in%20Delhi.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20official%20counts%2C%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%98legal%E2%80%99%20street%20vendors%20in%20Delhi%20is%20only%201%2C25%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hearings%20held%20amongst%20street%20vendors%20of%20Delhi%20revealed%20that%20their%20income%20from%20vending%20came%20down%20by%2050%25-70%25%20since%20the%20pandemic%20and%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20recovered%20from%20the%20financial%20distress.%20The%20surge%20in%20online%20shopping%20further%20worsened%20their%20economic%20distress.%20Not%20having%20much%20of%20a%20choice%20but%20to%20rely%20on%20money%20lenders%2C%20most%20of%20them%20currently%20face%20spiralling%20debts.%20They%20also%20disclosed%20that%20the%20biggest%20distress%20they%20faced%20and%20continue%20to%20experience%20is%20forceful%20evictions%20and%20harassment%20by%20the%20MCD%20and%20police%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20after%20the%20lockdown%20was%20lifted%2C%20police%20and%20MCD%20officials%20forcefully%20closed%20my%20shop%206-7%20times.%20I%20have%20all%20the%20documents%20required%20for%20vending.%20But%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20to%20them%20if%20you%20refuse%20to%20pay%20them%20a%20bribe%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Neeta%20from%20Kalkaji.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20state%20that%20her%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%20was%20disrupted%20as%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20a%20smartphone.%20She%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%201%2C50%2C000%20during%20the%20pandemic%20to%20sustain%20her%20family%20which%20she%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20repay%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20work%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20my%20shop%20was%20closed%20for%20eight%20months.%20When%20I%20reopened%2C%20MCD%20officials%20ceased%20my%20goods%2015%20times.%20Officials%20would%20keep%20harassing%20us%20and%20issue%20challans%20for%20no%20reason.%20They%20called%20me%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Echuda%20chamar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(casteist%20slang)%20while%20speaking%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalled%20Ritu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Street%20Vendors%20Act%2C%202014%2C%20takes%20precedence%20over%20the%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Act%2C%201957%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Act%2C%201978.%20Despite%20this%2C%20a%20complete%20police%20state%20was%20witnessed%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20Vendors%20were%20mercilessly%20lathi-charged%20and%20arrested%20and%20their%20vending%20was%20disrupted%20even%20as%20the%20lockdown%20was%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETown%20Vending%20Committee%20(TVC)%20members%20said%20that%20despite%20being%20elected%20representatives%20of%20street%20vendors%2C%20they%20face%20hurdles.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20elected%20members%20and%20have%20been%20assigned%20the%20role%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Act.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20not%20informed%20about%20meetings.%20The%20recommendations%20and%20suggestions%20provided%20by%20us%20are%20not%20included%20in%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting.%20They%20mark%20our%20presence%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20attendance%20register%20and%20by%20the%20time%20we%20look%20at%20the%20minutes%2C%20we%20realise%20that%20notes%20have%20been%20added%20based%20on%20whims%20and%20fancies%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20a%20TVC%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20TVC%20member%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20faced%20difficulties%20as%20both%20street%20vendors%20and%20TVC%20members.%20If%20we%20as%20TVC%20members%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20any%20intervention%2C%20how%20can%20the%20street%20vendor%20community%20rely%20on%20the%20systems%20of%20democracy%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETVC%20members%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20surveying%20of%20vendors%20is%20not%20done%20effectively%2C%20which%20results%20in%20a%20section%20of%20vendors%20not%20being%20surveyed%20and%20not%20receiving%20the%20documents%20required%20for%20vending.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERatheesh%2C%20a%20BCom%20graduate%2C%20became%20a%20vendor%20because%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20job.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20shop%20was%20closed%20for%20two%20years%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20When%20I%20tried%20vending%2C%20police%20thrashed%20me%2C%20and%20my%20leg%20was%20fractured.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20surveyed%2C%20because%20of%20which%20he%20has%20to%20discreetly%20run%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20were%20their%20means%20of%20livelihood%20hanging%20by%20a%20thread%2C%20they%20also%20incurred%20additional%20expenses%20as%20the%20police%20lathi-charge%20often%20caused%20them%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20relief%20schemes%20such%20as%20the%20PM%20SVANidhi%20loan%20introduced%20to%20aid%20vendors%20were%20well%20received%2C%20vendors%20say%20that%20those%20weren%E2%80%99t%20as%20effective%20or%20even%20easily%20accessible.%20During%20an%20already%20tumultuous%20time%2C%20vendors%20found%20themselves%20going%20from%20one%20office%20to%20another%20trying%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20loan.%20Banks%20often%20turned%20their%20backs%20and%20refused%20to%20assist%20those%20in%20need.%20During%20the%20Parliament%20session%2C%20the%20housing%20and%20urban%20affairs%20minister%20disclosed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsonair.com%2F2023%2F08%2F03%2F38-lakh-street-vendors-benefited-from-pm-svanidhi-scheme-says-housing-urban-affairs-minister-hardeep-singh-puri%2F%5C%22%3E38%20lakh%3C%2Fa%3E%20vendors%20benefitted%20from%20the%20PM%20SVANidhi%20scheme.%20Our%20interaction%20with%20the%20vendors%20revealed%20that%20while%20some%20of%20them%20did%20receive%20the%20amount%2C%20others%20struggled%20to%20get%20their%20loan%20approved%20and%20another%20section%20is%20still%20waiting%20for%20the%20disbursement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaste%20pickers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20home%20to%20over%20four%20million%20waste%20pickers%20and%20Delhi%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20over%20two%20lakh%20waste%20pickers.%20Over%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1007651%2Fdelhi-master-plan-2041-is-there-space-for-waste-workers%5C%22%3E%2042%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20waste%20pickers%20in%20Delhi%20segregate%20waste%20in%20their%20homes%20or%20by%20the%20roadside%20as%20they%20have%20no%20allotted%20space%20to%20work%20in.%20Waste%20pickers%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20keeping%20our%20cities%20clean.%20Yet%2C%20they%20live%20and%20work%20in%20abject%20conditions.%20Living%20in%20rag-tag%20tents%20with%20piles%20of%20collected%20garbage%20all%20around%20their%20living%20space%2C%20they%20have%20no%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20sewage%20or%20toilet%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHearings%20held%20amongst%20waste%20pickers%20of%20Delhi%20revealed%20that%20they%20had%20no%20income%20and%20savings%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20They%20relied%20on%20moneylenders%20which%20also%20increased%20their%20debts.%20Besides%2C%20they%20were%20charged%20by%20the%20municipal%20authorities%20for%20collecting%20the%20waste%20they%20were%20entitled%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20no%20income%20during%20the%20lockdown%20as%20army%20personnel%20were%20around%20torturing%20and%20beating%20people%20arbitrarily.%20This%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20fear%20and%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20work.%20We%20relied%20on%20moneylenders%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20We%20struggle%20to%20make%20monthly%20interest%20payments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranjith%20from%20Bhuapur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20were%20told%20not%20to%20venture%20out%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20lockdown%2C%20waste%20pickers%2C%20whose%20livelihood%20required%20getting%20out%20and%20collecting%20waste%2C%20were%20caught%20in%20a%20limbo.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20government%20support%20in%20terms%20of%20free%20ration.%20No%20scheme%20was%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nivin%20from%20Bhalaswa.%20He%20further%20stated%20that%20government%20officials%20only%20visit%20when%20they%20want%20votes.%20Another%20observation%20from%20the%20hearing%20was%20that%20the%20pandemic%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20further%20the%20trend%20of%20MCD%20privatising%20waste%20management%20and%20contractualisation%20of%20waste%20pickers.%20Waste%20pickers%20had%20to%20find%20means%20to%20survive%20as%20they%20had%20little%20to%20no%20help%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20COVID-19%20didn%E2%80%99t%20spread%20amongst%20the%20community%2C%20the%20lockdown%20that%20was%20in%20place%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20many%20of%20them%20to%20access%20regular%20health%20services.%20They%20even%20had%20to%20work%20without%20protective%20gear%20while%20segregating%20used%20masks%2C%20Covid%20testing%20kits%2C%20syringes%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeavers%20being%20pushed%20out%20of%20traditional%20weaving%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20handloom%20sector%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20informal%20sector%20in%20India.%20According%20to%20the%20Handloom%20Census%202019-20%2C%20there%20are%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1806546%5C%22%3E%203.5%20million%20%3C%2Fa%3Eworkers%20in%20the%20handloom%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHearings%20held%20amongst%20handloom%20workers%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20revealed%20that%20the%20pandemic%20had%20an%20impact%20on%20their%20livelihood.%20They%20went%20for%20months%20without%20work%2C%20getting%20pushed%20into%20abject%20poverty%20and%20starvation.%20This%20led%20some%20weavers%20to%20switch%20jobs%20and%20move%20places%20to%20find%20better-paying%20jobs.%20The%20exploitation%20by%20master%20weavers%20worsened%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20pandemic%2C%20master%20weavers%20have%20reduced%20our%20wage%20per%20saree.%20We%20are%20looking%20for%20other%20job%20opportunities%20as%20income%20from%20weaving%20isn%E2%80%99t%20keeping%20our%20family%20afloat%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nimi%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20She%20further%20stated%20that%20her%20husband%20passed%20away%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20but%20the%20family%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20received%20Covid%20death%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20disclosed%20during%20the%20hearings%20that%20the%20industry%20struggled%20with%20the%20GST%20imposition.%20Before%202017%2C%20handloom%20products%20were%20either%20not%20taxed%20or%20were%20taxed%20at%20low%20rates.%20However%2C%20with%20GST%20being%20imposed%20on%20handloom%20products%2C%20they%20are%20taxed%20anywhere%20from%205%25%20and%2018%25.%20The%20GST%20rule%20states%20that%20aside%20from%20the%20finished%20cloth%2C%20all%20materials%20used%20in%20the%20production%2C%20including%20yarn%2C%20thread%2C%20etc.%20will%20attract%20a%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20the%20economic%20crisis%20was%20high%2C%20weavers%20struggled%20to%20buy%20materials%20for%20weaving%20because%20of%20taxes.%20They%20further%20revealed%20that%20as%20many%20of%20them%20lack%20education%2C%20they%20struggle%20with%20the%20technical%20side%20of%20filing%20GST.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20later%2C%20as%20pressure%20mounted%20on%20the%20government%20to%20relieve%20weavers%20from%20economic%20distress%2C%20the%20GST%20was%20rolled%20back%20to%205%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sector%20also%20faces%20stiff%20competition%20with%20the%20powerloom%20industry%20as%20the%20latter%20has%20almost%20entirely%20taken%20over%20the%20traditional%20handloom%20industry.%20Handloom%20workers%20assert%20that%20the%20powerloom%20industry%20is%20encroaching%20upon%20the%20handloom%20sector%20by%20disregarding%20the%20Handloom%20Reservation%20Act%2C%201985.%20As%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20the%20production%20of%20certain%20products%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20handloom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COfficials%20take%20bribes%20from%20powerloom%20owners%20and%20refuse%20to%20take%20action%20against%20those%20violating%20the%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20weaver.%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20Handloom%20Reservation%20Act%20has%20been%20a%20long%20pending%20demand%20of%20handloom%20weavers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20quest%20for%20answers%20and%20relief%20measures%20from%20the%20authorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20of%2013%20public%20hearings%20across%20four%20states%20had%20marginalised%20sections%20coming%20forward%20to%20speak%20in%20a%20room%20full%20of%20people.%20This%20is%20testimony%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20distress%20and%20impact%20of%20the%20pandemic%20still%20linger%2C%20and%20they%20relive%20every%20moment%20of%20the%20pandemic%20like%20it%20happened%20yesterday.%20These%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society%20need%20answers%20from%20the%20government%20authorities%20as%20to%20why%20they%20were%20not%20protected%20and%20cared%20for%20and%20were%20thrown%20to%20death%2C%20debt%20and%20distress.%20They%20also%20demand%20robust%20relief%20measures%20from%20the%20government%20to%20stabilise%20their%20lives%20impacted%20by%20the%20pandemic.%20There%20ought%20to%20be%20accountability%20and%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20one-way%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENames%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EV.R.%20Sreya%20is%20a%20researcher%20associated%20with%20People%E2%80%99s%20Commission%20and%20Public%20Inquiry%20Committee%20process.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695292238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F21194948%2FScreen-Shot-2020-05-21-at-7.49.32-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fis-the-pandemic-really-over-unearthing-stories-of-death-debt-and-distress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marginalised%20sections%20are%20still%20feeling%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20pandemic%20%E2%80%93%20and%20still%20waiting%20for%20answers%20from%20the%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fis-the-pandemic-really-over-unearthing-stories-of-death-debt-and-distress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak's%20general%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20in%20last%20week%20of%20Jan%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695292065000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103836759%2Cimgsize-531174.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistans-general-elections-to-be-held-in-last-week-of-january-2024%2Farticleshow%2F103836761.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20has%20announced%20that%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20January%202024.%20The%20commission%20has%20completed%20its%20review%20of%20the%20constituency%20delimitation%20process%20and%20will%20release%20the%20initial%20list%20on%20September%2027.%20After%20considering%20objections%20and%20suggestions%2C%20the%20final%20list%20will%20be%20issued%20on%20November%2030.%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20experiencing%20political%20unrest%20since%20the%20removal%20of%20f