ons%2C%20especially%20in%20Canada.%20Khalistani%20separatism%20finds%20little%20hold%20in%20the%20Sikh%20homeland%20of%20India.%20Yet%2C%20referendums%20demanding%20a%20separate%20state%20of%20Khalistan%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20are%20regularly%20held%20with%20political%20patronage%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20deadliest%20terror%20attack%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20-%20the%201985%20Kanishka%20Airlines%20bombing%20that%20killed%20over%20300%2C%20including%2085%20children%20-%20Jagmeet%20Singh%2C%20a%20political%20partner%20of%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20is%20a%20supporter%20of%20Khalistan.%20He%20is%20essential%20to%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20premiership%20and%20leverages%20the%20Sikh%20population%20in%20Canada%20as%20a%20voting%20bloc%20to%20maintain%20support%20for%20the%20Liberal%20Party%20of%20Canada.%20The%20Sikhs%20are%20a%20small%20but%20rapidly%20growing%20minority%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20Sikhs%20migrating%20to%20Canada%20gain%20asylum%20by%20leveraging%20a%20loophole%20in%20Canadian%20immigration%20law%2C%20with%20some%20help%20from%20separatists%20in%20Punjab.%20Essentially%2C%20the%20Khalistanis%20have%20functioned%20as%20an%20immigration%20scam%20at%20scale%2C%20but%20changes%20Canadian%20demographics%20for%20Trudeau's%20politics%20favourably.%20Unfortunately%2C%20that%20is%20not%20all%20it%20has%20functioned%20as.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20responsible%20for%20the%20death%20of%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20as%20well%20as%20a%20sitting%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20radicalised%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20have%20been%20responsible%20for%20targeted%20killings%20on%20Canadian%20and%20Indian%20soil%20even%20recently%2C%20and%20show%20disproportionate%20presence%20in%20Canada's%20drug%20trade%20and%20human%20trafficking%20gangs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ffneil63o_pm-modi-justin-trudeau-_625x300_11_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20has%20repeatedly%20urged%20Canada%20to%20act%20against%20Khalistani%20terror%2C%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20refrained%20from%20taking%20a%20confrontational%20diplomatic%20position%2C%20hoping%20for%20future%20cooperation%20with%20Canada.%20The%20tit-for-tat%20action%20after%20Canada%20expelled%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%20over%20unfounded%20allegations%20of%20a%20role%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20separatist%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20seems%20to%20have%20caught%20Justin%20Trudeau%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20India%20suspended%20visa%20services%20in%20Canada%20citing%20%26quot%3Boperational%20reasons%26quot%3B.%20So%20far%2C%20New%20Delhi's%20actions%20included%20expelling%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20and%20a%20Canadian%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20and%20issuing%20an%20advisory%20for%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20awkwardness%20surrounding%20Trudeau's%20visit%20to%20India%20for%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Trudeau%20did%20not%20get%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%3B%20his%20%26quot%3Bpull-aside%26quot%3B%20talks%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20were%20also%20strained%20by%20the%20Khalistan%20row.%20Canada%20paused%20a%20possible%20trade%20deal%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20fiasco%2C%20Trudeau%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20an%20additional%20two%20days%20in%20Delhi%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20snag%20in%20his%20plane.%20The%20Canadian%20opposition%20tore%20into%20him%20for%20his%20lacklustre%20international%20presence%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20being%20an%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20country.%20His%20means%20of%20making