wers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Netflix%20film%20hinges%20on%20a%20single%20mother%20and%20her%2013-year-old%20school-going%20daughter%20who%20are%20drawn%20into%20a%20calculated%20but%20risky%20cover-up%20attempt%20and%20a%20police%20investigation%20that%20hits%20a%20trail%20that%20nearly%20goes%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20taut%20script%2C%20spiffy%20dialogues%20(by%20Ghosh%20and%20Raj%20Vasant)%2C%20first-rate%20performances%20and%20a%20keen%20sense%20of%20place%20serve%20to%20enhance%20the%20mystery%20that%20surrounds%20a%20lonesome%20math%20teacher%20who%20goes%20about%20his%20daily%20chores%20with%20mechanical%20detachment%20and%20a%20woman%20who%20moves%20in%20next%20door%20and%20becomes%20an%20object%20of%20silent%2C%20obsession%20for%20the%20reclusive%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20third%20novel%20of%20Keigo%20Higashino's%20Detective%20Galileo%20series%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Devotion%20of%20Suspect%20X%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jaane%20Jaan%20takes%20only%20a%20few%20minutes%20to%20deliver%20the%20watershed%20moment%20from%20which%20everything%20else%20in%20the%20plot%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20suspense%20stems%20from%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20are%20set%20in%20motion%20by%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%20that%20tests%20the%20math%20teacher's%20genius%20and%20puts%20his%20neighbour's%20future%20under%20a%20cloud.%3Cem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjaane-jaan-trailer-the-curious-case-of-kareena-kapoor-vijay-varma-and-jaideep-ahlawat-4361066%5C%22%3EJaane%20Jaan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20genre-bending%20police%20procedural%20that%20dissects%20the%20minds%20of%20three%20characters%20rather%20than%20play%20out%20like%20a%20standard%20whodunit%20(in%20any%20case%2C%20we%20know%20who%20from%20the%20very%20outset).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaya%20D'Souza%20(Kareena%20Kapoor%20in%20her%20OTT%20debut)%20has%20escaped%20an%20unhappy%20past%20and%20settled%20into%20a%20stable%20life%20that%20revolves%20around%20her%20daughter%20and%20a%20thriving%20cafe%20in%20Kalimpong.%20Naren%20Vyas%20(Jaideep%20Ahlawat)%20is%20in%20love%20with%20mathematics%20more%20than%20with%20anything%20else%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%20detective%20Karan%20Anand%20(Vijay%20Varma)%2C%20sent%20to%20Kalimpong%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20is%20the%20only%20one%20who%20puts%20all%20his%20cards%20on%20the%20table.%20He%20is%20in%20search%20of%20a%20wanted%20man.%20With%20no%20emotional%20or%20psychological%20baggage%20weighing%20him%20down%2C%20he%20gets%20down%20to%20work%20with%20a%20local%20policeman%2C%20Sub-inspector%20Sundar%20Singh%20(Karma%20Takapa%2C%20who%20loses%20no%20opportunity%20to%20make%20his%20presence%20felt).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Maya's%20past%20returns%20to%20hound%20her%2C%20the%20well-being%20of%20her%20daughter%20Tara%20(Naisha%20Khanna)%20becomes%20her%20priority.%20She%20finds%20an%20unlikely%20ally%20in%20Naren%2C%20who%20is%20awkwardly%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20life%20beyond%20math%20and%20his%20evening%20jujitsu%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20transpires%20that%20Karan%20and%20Naren%20were%20classmates.%20As%20the%20two%20men%20probe%20each%20other's%20susceptibilities%2C%20the%20cop%20is%20under%20increasing%20pressure%20from%20his%20boss%20to%20find%20a%20corrupt%20policeman%20and%20hawala%20racket%20kingpin%2C%20Ajit%20Mhatre%20(Saurabh%20Sachdeva%20in%20a%20terrific%20cameo)%2C%20who%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20Kalimpong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20precise%20world%20building%20and%20the%20measured%20dialogues%20-%20a%20Hindi%20crime%20drama%20for%20once%20steers%20clear%20of%20cuss%20words%20-%20make%20the%20battle%20of%20wits%20between%20the%20two%20men%20consistently%20gripping%20and%20intriguing%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20audience%20is%20in%20the%20know%20of%20what%20is%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20swept%20under%20the%20carpet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELove%20or%2C%20to%20be%20precise%2C%20infatuation%20that%20inches%20dangerously%20close%20to%20stalking%2C%20finds%20an%20exceedingly%20strange%20way%20of%20expressing%20itself%20in%20Naren's%20case%2C%20while%20a%20hint%20of%20lust%20colours%20Karan's%20exchanges%20with%20Maya%2C%20his%20prime%20suspect.%20Obsession%2C%20jealousy%20and%20anguish%20are%20all%20at%20play%20as%20the%20trio%20tread%20on%20ethically%20slippery%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wall%20around%20the%20uncommunicative%20math%20teacher%2C%20an%20inscrutable%20enigma%20locked%20in%20an%20unbreakable%20shell%2C%20is%20like%20the%20mist%20that%20hangs%20over%20f%20Kalimpong.%20It%20hides%20a%20great%20deal%20even%20as%20it%20constantly%20shifts%20to%20reveal%20hitherto%20hidden%20nooks%20and%20vistas.%20Karan%20nearly%20gives%20up%20on%20the%20case%2C%20having%20hit%20his%20head%20against%20the%20wall%20a%20few%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaya%20has%20to%20hold%20her%20ground%20through%20it%20all%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20dichotomies%20that%20confront%20her.%20Her%20assistant%20Prema%20(Lin%20Laishram)%20claims%20that%20their%20cafe%20makes%20the%20best%20momos%20in%20town.%20But%20it%20isn't%20for%20the%20dumplings%20that%20Naren%20makes%20his%20way%20to%20the%20eatery%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20staid%2C%20painfully%20shy%20Naren%20has%20a%20receding%20hairline%2C%20looks%20older%20than%20he%20is%20and%20walks%20like%20a%20man%20who%20would%20rather%20let%20time%20pass%20him%20by.%20He%20plays%20chess%20with%20himself%20and%20sets%20question%20papers%20so%20tough%20that%20the%20school%20authorities%20request%20him%20to%20take%20it%20easy.%20But%20he%20has%20his%20reasons.%20Pull%20yourself%20higher%2C%20the%20world%20will%20not%20descend%20to%20your%20level%2C%20Naren%20tells%20a%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaane%20Jaan%20explores%20the%20debilitating%20isolation%20of%20a%20man%20lost%20in%20his%20own%20world%20as%20well%20as%20the%20pitfalls%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20woman%20determined%20to%20put%20her%20troubled%20past%20behind%20her.%20Multiple%20dualities%20-%20protector-predator%2C%20victim-perpetrator%2C%20friend-foe%20and%20genius-oddball%20-%20are%20central%20to%20the%20twisted%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20title%2C%20which%20might%20suggest%20that%20this%20is%20a%20story%20with%20an%20undercurrent%20of%20romance%2C%20comes%20from%20one%20of%20the%20rare%20cabaret%20numbers%20that%20Lata%20Mangeshkar%20sang%20(Intaqam%2C%201969%2C%20filmed%20on%20Helen).%20The%20song%20plays%20in%20a%20karaoke%20bar%20and%20provides%20a%20fleeting%20glimpse%20of%20Maya's%20back%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGHX6yT9Lxfo%3Fsi%3D9jr5GO50X8pgLfHp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaane%20Jaan%20is%20laced%20with%20a%20slew%20of%20retro%20songs%20from%20other%20decades%20of%20Hindi%20film%20music.%20Some%20of%20them%20play%20so%20faintly%20that%20they%20are%20almost%20inaudible.%20Anirban%20Sengupta's%20sound%20design%20and%20the%20background%20score%20by%20Shor%20Police%20(Clinton%20Cerejo%20and%20Bianca%20Gomes)%20add%20appreciable%20allure%20to%20the%20film's%20soundscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20songs%20may%20seem%20a%20tad%20arbitrary%2C%20but%20they%20together%20hark%20back%20to%20an%20era%20of%20perennially%20popular%20Hindi%20film%20music%20even%20as%20it%20points%20to%20-%20at%20least%20a%20handful%20of%20the%20numbers%20do%20-%20what%20the%20female%20protagonist%20of%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20running%20away%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEditor%20Urvashi%20Saxena%20creates%20crisp%20and%20aptly%20complex%20patterns%20as%20she%20intercuts%20scenes%20into%20each%20other%20all%20through%20the%20film.%20Cinematographer%20Avik%20Mukhopadhyay%20locates%20the%20mystique%20of%20Kalimpong%20in%20everyday%20settings%20without%20resorting%20to%20any%20obtrusive%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKareena%20