er%20the%20staff%20started%20wearing%20it.%20There%20have%20been%20several%20complaints%20from%20the%20security%20staff%20stating%20that%20they%20were%20sweating%20profusely%20due%20to%20the%20fabric%20used%20and%20the%20design%20of%20the%20new%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20500-odd%20parliament%20security%20staff%20turned%20up%20to%20work%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20their%20usual%20navy%20blue%20safari%20suits.%20Though%20no%20official%20reason%20was%20stated%20for%20withdrawing%20the%20uniform%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-security-staff-complain-about-new-uniforms%2Farticle67326130.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20many%20staffers%20have%20refused%20to%20wear%20the%20new%20outfit%20given%20its%20design%20and%20fabric%20out%20of%20which%20it%20is%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20parliament%20has%20been%20shifted%20to%20a%20new%20building%2C%20the%20government%20came%20up%20with%20new%20uniforms%20for%20the%20staff%20working%20there.%20While%20the%20security%20staff%E2%80%99s%20uniform%20has%20been%20designed%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20army%20camouflage%20fatigues%2C%20those%20who%20work%20inside%20the%20House%20on%20legislative%20work%20have%20been%20assigned%20cream%20jackets%2C%20cream%20shirts%2C%20and%20khaki%20trousers%20with%20pink%20lotus%20printed%20on%20them.%20Chamber%20attendants%2C%20officers%2C%20security%20personnel%2C%20drivers%2C%20and%20marshals%20have%20been%20assigned%20new%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20latest%20order%2C%20only%20the%20new%20uniform%20of%20the%20security%20staff%20has%20been%20withdrawn%2C%20while%20other%20staffers%20will%20have%20to%20continue%20to%20don%20their%20respective%20new%20uniforms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fparliament-security-staffs-uniform-withdrawn%2Farticleshow%2F103823346.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of