ilable.%20Some%20of%20us%20got%20the%20uniform%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20boots%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOthers%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20design%20of%20the%20new%20outfit%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20new%20uniform%20does%20not%20go%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20parliament%2C%20for%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20combat%20outfit%20worn%20by%20armed%20forces.%20They%20said%20parliament%20security%20staff%20fall%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20civilian%20staff%2C%20for%20their%20role%20is%20limited%20to%20facilitate%20MPs%20at%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20officials%20even%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20uniform%20is%20what%20usually%20armed%20forces%20wear%20during%20combat.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20eerily%20looks%20like%20the%20uniform%20worn%20by%20Pakistani%20Rangers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20news%20of%20new%20uniforms%20for%20parliament%20staffers%20has%20been%20around%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20launched%20criticism%20against%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20just%20reducing%20the%20security%20personnel%20to%20showpieces%20to%20please%20the%20ruler%2C%20this%20government%20has%20also%20cut%2025%2C000%20from%20each%20of%20the%20600%20Parliament%20security%20staff%20for%20this%20uniform.%20Why%20should%20our%20security%20personnel%20suffer%20for%20the%20Rule%E2%80%99s%20fancy%20dress%20competition%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20Congress%20whip%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENot%20just%20reducing%20the%20security%20personnel%20to%20showpieces%20to%20please%20the%20Ruler%2C%20this%20Govt%20has%20also%20cut%2025%2C000%20from%20each%20of%20the%20600%20Parliament%20Security%20staff%20for%20this%20%E2%80%98uniform%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20should%20our%20security%20personnel%20suffer%20for%20the%20Ruler%E2%80%99s%20fancy%