t%20year%20-%20and%20verdicts%20are%20rolling%20in%20on%20the%20first%20demo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fnewsbeat-66842873%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fnewsbeat-66842873.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fnewsbeat-66842873.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCorruption%20Begins%20With%20Voter%20Bribery%26quot%3B%3A%20India's%202nd%20Richest%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArunachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Pema%20Khandu%20has%20exhorted%20voters%20to%20join%20his%20campaign%20against%20%26quot%3Bmoney%20culture%26quot%3B%20in%20elections%20and%20help%20him%20make%20the%20next%20polls%20about%20performance%20and%20not%20money.%20The%20BJP%20leader%20has%20also%20said%20that%20a%20politician%20who%20expends%20crores%20on%20getting%20elected%20will%20spend%20the%20next%20five%20years%20trying%20to%20recover%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20election%20watchdog%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%2C%20Mr%20Khandu%20is%20the%20second-richest%20chief%20minister%20in%20India%20with%20assets%20of%20over%20Rs%20163%20crore%20declared%20in%20his%20election%20affidavit.%20At%2044%2C%20he%20is%20also%20the%20country's%20youngest%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20big%20public%20meeting%20at%20Yachuli%20in%20Lower%20Subansiri%20district%2C%20Mr%20Khandu%20urged%20people%20to%20help%20him%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20next%20year%20are%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20performance%20and%20not%20money%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20complain%20against%20corruption.%20But%20have%20we%20ever%20thought%20where%20it%20begins%3F%20It%20begins%20when%20a%20voter%20casts%20his%20or%20her%20valuable%20vote%20in%20exchange%20for%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chi