ism%20and%20Neurodevelopmental%20Disorders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20she%20is%20up%20against%2C%20though%20%E2%80%93%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20Shambhu%20Prasad%20Acharya%2C%20one%20of%20the%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20senior-most%20officials%20%E2%80%93%20may%20also%20be%20expecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20vote%2C%20given%20the%20close%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20matters%20who%20becomes%20their%20regional%20directors%20because%20they%20have%20considerable%20decentralised%20authority%20to%20influence%20the%20health%20chances%20of%20billions%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealthpolicy-watch.news%2Fshenanigans-in-who-south-east-asia-as-politicians-daughter-contests-for-election-as-regional-director%2F%5C%22%3EHealth%20Policy%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElections%20to%20appoint%20the%20WHO%20South%20East%20Asia%20Regional%20Office%20(SEARO)%20director%20will%20be%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20SEARO%20is%20based%2C%20between%20October%2030%20and%20November%202.%20Eleven%20countries%20will%20be%20voting%3A%20Bangladesh%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20North%20Korea%2C%20India%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Maldives%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Timor-Leste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20speculation%20that%20Wazed%20may%20soon%20be%20taking%20on%20a%20more%20active%20role%20in%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20Awami%20League.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20of%20a%20succession%20plan%20in%20Awami%20League%20has%20long%20been%20thought%20about.%20We%20believe%20that%20it%20will%20be%20done%20in%20a%20democratic%20manner%2C%20but%20democracy%20does%20not%20eliminate%20familial%20ties%20that%20a%20person%20may%20have%20with%20a%20political%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ambassador%20Sarvajit%20Chakravarti%2C%20who%20served%20two%20terms%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fworld%2Fsheikh-hasinas-daughter-joins-her-in-g20-summit-speculation-rife-on-possible-political-role-2678315%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHasina%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20take%20Wazed%20along%20to%20high-level%20international%20meetings%2C%20including%20the%20G20%2C%20has%20come%20under%20scrutiny.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6being%20introduced%20by%20her%20mother%20at%20recent%20high-level%20summits%20such%20as%20BRICS%2C%20ASEAN%2C%20G20%20and%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20to%20craft%20deals%20in%20exchange%20for%20votes%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20crossing%20the%20fine%20line%20between%20a%20government%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20lobbying%20for%20its%20candidate%20and%20craven%20nepotism%2C%E2%80%9D%20Health%20Policy%20Watch%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20also%20alleged%20that%20Bangladesh%20had%20put%20pressure%20on%20other%20countries%20not%20to%20nominate%20candidates%2C%20and%20that%20there%20was%20also%20pressure%20on%20Nepal%20to%20withdraw%20Acharya%E2%80%99s%20candidature.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20yet%20to%20decide%20how%20it%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fin-a-tough-choice-sheikh-hasinas-daughter-nepal-who-veteran-go-head-to-head-for-indias-vote%2Farticle67278193.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20but%20some%20officials%20say%20Wazed%20may%20have%20an%20edge%20because%20of%20the%20close%20and%20important%20India-Bangladesh%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695285042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21133713%2FF5guFiCXcAACIIW.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbangladesh-pm-sheikh-hasinas-daughter-up-against-nepals-nominee-in-who-regional-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hasina's%20decision%20to%20take%20Wazed%20along%20to%20high-level%20international%20meetings%2C%20including%20the%20G20%2C%20has%20come%20under%20scrutiny.