%3E%20quoted%20Malik%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Malik%20has%20spoken%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20accountability%20in%20this%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatya-pal-malik-full-interview-pulwama-modi%5C%22%3Eexplosive%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Malik%20had%20said%20that%20the%20CRPF%20had%20asked%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20for%20aircraft%20to%20ferry%20their%20people%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20such%20a%20big%20convoy%20never%20goes%20by%20road.%E2%80%9D%20The%20home%20ministry%20refused%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20told%20it%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20this%20has%20happened%20due%20to%20our%20fault.%20Had%20we%20given%20the%20aircraft%2C%20this%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20happened.%20To%20which%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20should%20keep%20quiet%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20NSO%20Ajit%20Doval%20had%20also%20said%20this%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalik%20also%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceight%20to%2010%20link%20roads%20were%20unmanned%E2%80%9D%2C%20pointing%20to%20an%20overall%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pulwama%20attack%20had%20taken%20place%20just%20months%20before%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20carried%20out%20airstrikes%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Balakot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Malik%20disagreed%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20the%20phrasing%20that%20Modi%20used%20the%20attack%20to%20leverage%20his%20re-election%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20language%2C%20I%20can%20just%20say%20that%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20the%20root%20cause%20or%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20that%20matter%2C%20or%20maybe%20if%20we%20also%20went%20to%20the%20start%20and%20completely%20in