e%20not%20just%20preventing%20marriages%3B%20we%E2%80%99re%20saving%20lives.%20These%20young%20girls%20now%20have%20a%20platform%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20While%20I%E2%80%99m%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20development%20projects%2C%20this%20one%20is%20particularly%20dear%20to%20me.%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripura%20is%20notorious%20for%20child%20marriages%20with%20four%20in%2010%20girls%20getting%20married%20before%20turning%2018.%20In%20a%20novel%20approach%2C%20South%20Tripura%20District%20Magistrate%20Saju%20Vaheed%20revived%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Manch%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%20cum%20platform%20to%20prevent%20young%20girls%20from%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20and%20getting%20married.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Will%20Help%20You%20Find%20Less%20Crowded%20Fuel%20Stations%2C%20For%20CNG%20%26amp%3B%20EVs%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20his%20licence%20at%2018%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20tried%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306067%2Fcollege-dropout-launches-ev-startup-builds-made-in-india-luxury-electric-suv-pravaig%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20a%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20every%20other%20person.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20often%20end%20up%20getting%20into%20accidents%2C%20and%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20other%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stop%20driving.%20This%20made%20him%20a%20regular%20user%20of%20cab%20services%20like%20Ola%20and%20Uber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20roads%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20which%20aimed%20to%20decongest%20fuel%20stations%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Vaibhav%2C%20an%20engineer%20from%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20was%20doing%20an%20internship%20in%20Greater%20Noida.%20During%20the%20half-hour%20commute%20between%20his%20home%20and%20office%2C%20he%20used%20to%20strike%20up%20conversations%20with%20cab%20drivers.%20They%20mainly%20drove%20CNG%20vehicles%20and%20this%20is%20where%20he%20learnt%20about%20their%20biggest%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20drivers%20complained%20of%20one%20single%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20the%20line%20at%20the%20fuel%20station%20was%20very%20long.%20Out%20of%20the%2010%20hours%20they%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20an%20hour%20was%20wasted%20at%20these%20fuel%20stations%20daily.%20The%20cab%20drivers%20told%20me%20that%20they%20lost%2010%20percent%20of%20their%20daily%20earnings%20idling%20away%20in%20the%20queue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20be%20wonderful%20if%20the%20cab%20driver%20could%20know%20which%20fuel%20station%20had%20a%20lesser%20waiting%20time%3F%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20%E2%80%98Nawgati%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%2020%20then%2C%20and%20in%20his%20third-year%20of%20engineering%2C%20Vaibhav%20thought%20that%20this%20problem%20must%20have%20been%20solved%20by%20someone.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20solution%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20one%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20Aalaa