his%20data%20and%20metrics%20help%20companies%20increase%20sales%2C%20reduce%20recurring%20costs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders.%20They%20get%20access%20to%20the%20vehicles%20fuelling%20at%20their%20station%2C%20how%20much%20time%20each%20vehicle%20is%20waiting%2C%20how%20much%20time%20is%20spent%20on%20fuelling%20every%20vehicle%2C%20which%20dispensers%20are%20being%20used%20more%2C%20what%20are%20the%20inefficiencies%2C%20amongst%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENawgati%20works%20on%20a%20subscription-based%20model%20and%20charges%20fuel%20stations%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20starting%20from%20Rs%205000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%2C%20that%20is%20saving%20money%20for%20fuel%20companies%2C%20was%20built%20at%20BITS%20Pilani%20in%202019%2C%20through%20the%20college%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20program%2C%20Pilani%20Innovation%20%26amp%3B%20Entrepreneurship%20Development%20Society%20(PIEDS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20building%20the%20technology%2C%20we%20embarked%20on%20trial%20runs%20that%20led%20us%20to%20a%20pilot%20project%20with%20Indraprastha%20Gas%20Ltd%20(IGL)%20in%202021.%20We%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20valuable%20insights%20regarding%20the%20challenges%20encountered%20by%20the%20teams%20at%20CNG%20stations.%20We%20then%20made%20some%20changes%20to%20enhance%20Aaveg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pilot%2C%20IGL%20signed%20an%20annual%20contract%20with%20Nawgati.%20Today%2C%20Aaveg%20is%20live%20at%20IGL%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20outlets%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Mahanagar%20Gas%20(MGL)%20outlets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20GAIL%20Gas%2C%20Torrent%20Gas%2C%20JioBP%2C%20HP%20Gas%20among%20several%20other%20fuel%20companies%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20plan%20to%20onboard%2015%2C000%20fueling%20outlets%20within%20two%20years.%20The%20startup%20has%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20helps%20fuel%20pumps%20manage%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-headin