ation%20to%20navigate%20to%20a%20CNG%2Fpetrol%2Fdiesel%20station%20on%20your%20route%2C%20or%20find%20one%20closest%20to%20you.%20We%20have%20more%20than%20a%20million%20downloads%20on%20the%20app%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav%2C%20co-founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Nawgati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%204-year-old%20app%20is%20currently%20free%2C%20but%20the%20founders%20have%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20freemium%20model%20soon%2C%20where%20they%20would%20offer%20basic%20features%20for%20free%2C%20but%20charge%20for%20the%20premium%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20had%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%202%20and%20signed%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2067%20lakhs%20for%203%20percent%20equity.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20Nawgati%20and%20led%20to%20more%20dealers%20reaching%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20the%20department%20of%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20revolutionising%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%2C%20benefiting%20both%20fuel%20providers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%20Any%20new%20CNG%20station%20is%20now%20listed%20on%20our%20app%20too.%20This%20helps%20fuel%20stations%20get%20more%20sales.%20We%20have%2075000%20fuel%20stations%20listed%20on%20the%20app%20today.%20We%20are%20fuel%20agnostic%2C%20and%20also%20list%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERun%20by%20two%2025-year-olds%20and%20one%2024-year-old%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20become%20synonymous%20with%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20Nawgati%20to%20be%20the%20doctor%20for%20any%20fuel%20related%20probl