dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330245%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20Nellayapan%20had%20just%20completed%20an%20MSc%20in%20physics.%20His%20older%20sister%20was%20getting%20married%2C%20for%20which%20his%20parents%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20tea%2Fsnack%20stall%2C%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20time%20before%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20wedding.%20People%20refused%20to%20lend%20money.%20My%20parents%20managed%20the%20required%20money%20with%20great%20difficulty.%20Till%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20the%20moneylenders%20kept%20us%20hanging.%20I%20felt%20so%20insulted.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20resolved%20to%20achieve%20something%20big%20in%20life%2C%20so%20my%20parents%20would%20never%20have%20to%20face%20such%20a%20situation%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%E2%80%99s%20college%20senior%2C%20who%20was%20working%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20apprised%20him%20about%20the%20opportunities%20there.%20And%20the%20then%2023-year-old%20left%20for%20Nagaland%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket%20and%20big%20dreams%20in%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20four%20days%20to%20reach%20Nagaland.%20My%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecouldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20train%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%20had%20to%20pawn%20her%20last%20piece%20of%20jewellery%20%E2%80%94%20her%20nose%20ring%20%E2%80%94%20which%20got%20us%20Rs%202%2C000.%20I%20remember%20the%20bank%20manager%E2%80%99s%20expression%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20nose%20ring%2C%20knowing%20we%20had%20no%20other%20choice.%20I%20felt%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20the%20amount%20helped%20him%20with%20food%20and%20lodging%20for%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201991%2C%20he%20started%20his%20career%20as%20a%20private%20school%20teacher%20in%20Nagaland%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month.%20He%20shares%20that%20this%20money%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20cover%20his%20expenses%20as%20he%20sent%20some%20money%20back%20home%20too.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%20700%20per%20month%20for%20electricity%20and%20rent.%20How%20could%20I%20survive%20on%20just%20Rs%20300%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20taking%20tuition%20for%20school%20students%20to%20supplement%20my%20income.%20I%20used%20to%20tutor%20from%206%20am%20to%2010%20am%2C%20then%20attend%20school%20until%204%20pm%2C%20and%20return%20to%20tutor%20again%20until%206%20pm.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20managed%20for%20the%20first%20six%20years%20in%20private%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20the%20time%20when%20Nagaland%20was%20facing%20insurgency%20issues.%20But%20the%20teacher%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20that%20hinder%20his%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Nellayapan%20got%20a%20job%20as%20a%20postgraduate%20teacher%20in%20physics%20at%20the%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Dimapur.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20got%20married%20and%20remembers%20how%20they%20then%20put%20an%20asbestos%20roof%20on%20their%20house.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20burden%20of%20responsibility%20is%20often%20a%20blessing.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20school%20principal%20in%202012%20and%20continued%20working%20there%20till%202017.%20Then%2C%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20he%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20deputy%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20trailblazer%20in%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B's%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20of%20Nellayapan%E2%80%99s%20siblings%20are%20well-educated%20due%20to%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20efforts%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID%20hit%20the%20nation%2C%20Nagaland%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20states%20to%20embrace%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20even%20recognised%20by%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Co-operation%20and%20Development%20Education%20(OECD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202020%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20rolled%20out%20a%20tele%2Fonline%20education%20programme%20through%20which%20education%20was%20offered%20through%20TV%20(Doordarshan%2C%20Kohima)%20and%20radio%20(All%20India%20Radio%2C%20Kohima).%20In%20May%202020%2C%20they%20also%20offered%20educational%20content%20through%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20This%20programme%20was%20led%20by%20C%20Shanavas%20%E2%80%94%20principal%20director%20of%20school%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20supported%20by%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHeartiest%20congratulations%20to%20the%20awardees%20of%20Governor's%20Gold%20Medal%20and%20Governor's%20Commendation%20Certificate%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F74th_IndependenceDay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%2374th_IndependenceDay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqdEbUZl7OP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqdEbUZl7OP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20(%40Neiphiu_Rio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNeiphiu_Rio%2Fstatus%2F1294503464827944962%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20face%20network%20issues.%20So%20we%20ironed%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20reach%20every%20student%2C%20irrespective%20of%20network.%20We%20were%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20conduct%20online%20exams%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%205%E2%80%9312%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20commendation%20certificate%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20IAS%20officers%20like%20Shanavas%20was%20also%20a%20big%20motivation%20for%20Nellayapan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with%20many%20IAS%20officers.%20They%20are%20an%20inspiration%20for%20me%20and%20I