nology%20(ICT)%20initiative%2C%20she%20procured%20five%20computers%2C%20two%20LED%20projectors%20and%20two%20additional%20classrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICT%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20School%20Scheme%20was%20launched%20in%20December%202004%20to%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20secondary%20stage%20students%20to%20mainly%20build%20their%20capacity%20on%20ICT%20skills%20and%20make%20them%20learn%20through%20the%20computer-aided%20learning%20process.%20She%20proudly%20states%20that%20her%20students%20are%20now%20able%20to%20use%20computers%20proficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20an%20era%20of%20globalisation.%20To%20be%20a%20global%20citizen%2C%20digital%20education%20is%20a%20must.%20I%20want%20my%20students%20to%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20computers%20well%20and%20therefore%2C%20am%20exposing%20them%20to%20the%20technology%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20headmistress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20holistic%20education%20a%20must%20for%20this%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESmt.%20Archana%20Nooguri%2C%20a%20National%20Awardee%20Teacher%202023%20from%20Telangana%2C%20works%20on%20improving%20enrolment%20rates%20%26amp%3B%20reducing%20dropouts.%20She%20develops%20low-cost%20teaching-learning%20material.%20She%20involved%20the%20community%20in%20setting%20up%20water%20purification%20plant%2C%20library%20etc.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FOurTeachersOurPrerna%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23OurTeachersOurPrerna%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeU7InH6xFN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FeU7InH6xFN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20(%40EduMinOfIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEduMinOfIndia%2Fstatus%2F1699030560587608210%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5