0pledge%20for%20a%20brighter%2C%20more%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20coming%20generation%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F218760%2Findian-womens-cricket-team-t20-world-cup-final-inspiring-shafali-verma-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20sections%20break%20the%20circle%20of%20poverty%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20be%20environmentally%20sensitive.%20Education%20is%20the%20only%20way%20these%20goals%20can%20be%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmita%20Sarma%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Akshar%20School%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20collected%20and%20recycled%20about%201%2C200%20bottles%20and%206%2C43%2C600%20plastic%20wrappers%20so%20far%20from%20the%20school%20kids.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20school%20follows%20a%20unique%20style%20of%20education%20where%20they%20place%20the%20students%20in%20grades%20as%20per%20their%20academic%20aptitude%20and%20not%20their%20age%20as%20is%20done%20in%20traditional%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20education%20accessible%20to%20all%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Parmita%20was%20mostly%20raised%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20Assam.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20I%20had%20an%20inclination%20towards%20doing%20things%20for%20others.%20My%20family%20was%20very%20politically%20aware%2C%20which%20further%20pushed%20me%20to%20the%20path%20of%20social%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20social%20work%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20work%20in%20the%20field%20of%20education%20as%20I%20believe%20that%20education%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20process%20of%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%20I%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20a%20free%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3